channel.title: So i got a call from rogers
channel.description:
I wasn't home, I had to go pick up my new glasses..
so i come home, and i had left my cellphone at home.
i have an alert, says i have a voicemail.
I listen to it, its from like a 1800/1866 number, this is what it said
"yoyo u got bad viruz on ur cumpter so lol go to rogers/getprotected to klean ur computr if u dont has virus kleaned we wil disble ur interwebs for 48 hours LOL!!!11"
so lulz, i just scanned, dont got shite
watdo, call up rogers and bitch?
